🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to find sum of first 100 numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE sum_100()
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT;
    s INT := 0;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..100 LOOP
        s := s + i;
    END LOOP;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Sum = %', s;
END;
$$;


